For the price we paid (CAD$194.48/night plus $20/day for parking) , we expected breakfast to be included but was told when we got there, breakfast was an extra CAD$16/person.	It came for ~ 140 CAD which for location and service was a great value.	Overall, it was an okay stay, but we would not stay there again because it is not good value for money.	We found a very good rate for this stay, and would certainly stay here again (if the price is right).